reviewText: After watching it, I kind of enjoy this, but I don't like some of the acting.  I wish it could be a little better.  But on the other hand, I LOVE Esther Williams!  I find Esther Williams so awesome, but, if they put this on DVD sometime soon, I will get it.  I still think some of the acting is bad, I wish it was a 1983 redo, and a 1995 VHS!

I always have loved Esther Williams. I loved the swimming
and the idea that there was no swearing or sex or bad words
